**Intermediate (Month 3-6)**
- 3x per week
- Light weight (5-25 lbs)
- 3-4 sets each direction
- 15-25 reps per set
- Progressive overload weekly

**Advanced (Month 6+)**
- 3-4x per week
- Heavier weights (25-45+ lbs)
- 4 sets each direction
- Can incorporate harness work
- Volume and intensity progression

**Sample Weekly Split:**

**Day A (After Upper Body):**
- Neck curls: 4x20
- Neck extensions: 4x20
- Lateral flexion: 3x15 each side

**Day B (After Any Workout):**
- Neck harness work: 4x15
- Shrugs: 3x12
- Lateral flexion: 3x15 each side

