**Weeks 5-8: Progressive Overload**
- 3 sessions per week
- Increase weight by 2-5 lbs when you can complete all reps easily
- 3-4 sets per direction
- 15-25 reps per set

**Month 3+: Continued Progression**
- Consider neck harness for convenience
- Continue adding weight gradually
- Measure every 4 weeks
